Package controller

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Controller
    This is the interface for all the controller classes
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BookingController
    This class handles the control flow of movie booking for a movie goer
    BookingHistoryController
    This class controls the display of the booking history of a movie goer
    CinemaStaffController
    This class controls the login and main menu for the cinema staff
    Main
    This class is the main class of the application.
    MovieController
    This class controls the display of the movies and their details and reviews.
    MovieEditController
    This class controls the creation, modification and removal of movies
    MovieGoerController
    This class controls the signup, login and main menu for movie goers
    NavigationController
    This method controls the navigation between the controller classes
    PricingSchemeEditController
    This class controls the modification of the pricing scheme and the holiday list.
    ShowTimeController
    This class controls the display of all the available show times
    ShowTimeEditController
    This class controls the creation, modification and removal of showtimes
    TopMoviesController
    This class controls the display of the top 5 movies by ticket sales and overall reviewer's rating
    UserController
    This class controls the selection of the user portal when a user first opens the MOBLIMA application
